{"id": "art-142", "label": "Art. 142", "title": "Art. 142", "slug": "art-142", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 142 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1842248439\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2212\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1842248439\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Consiliul de <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span>\neste îns&#259;rcinat cu îndeplinirea tuturor actelor necesare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> utile pentru realizarea obiectului de activitate al\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, cu <span class=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span>\ncelor rezervate de <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i> pentru\nadunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1400763846\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2211\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1400763846\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> are urm&#259;toarele <span class=SpellE>competen&#355;e</span>\nde baz&#259;, care nu pot fi delegate directorilor:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1842171795\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2210\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1842171795\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)stabilirea <span class=SpellE>direc&#355;iilor</span>\nprincipale de activitate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de dezvoltare ale <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_876199820\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2209\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_876199820\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)stabilirea politicilor contabile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\na sistemului de control financiar, precum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\naprobarea planific&#259;rii financiare;</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1428607061\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2208\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1428607061\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)numirea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> revocarea\ndirectorilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> stabilirea <span class=SpellE>remunera&#355;iei</span>\nlor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2126452523\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2207\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2126452523\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)supravegherea <span class=SpellE>activit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndirectorilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1165710667\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2206\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1165710667\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)preg&#259;tirea raportului anual, organizarea\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> implementarea hot&#259;rârilor acesteia;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_469907246\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2205\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_469907246\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)introducerea cererii pentru deschiderea procedurii <span\nclass=SpellE>insolven&#355;ei</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>,\npotrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legii</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>85/2006</span><span style='color:black'> privind\nprocedura <span class=SpellE>insolven&#355;ei</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_280231036\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2204\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_280231036\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)De asemenea, nu pot fi delegate directorilor <span\nclass=SpellE>atribu&#355;iile</span> primite de c&#259;tre consiliul de <span\nclass=SpellE>administra&#355;ie</span> din partea adun&#259;rii generale a <span\nclass=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, în conformitate cu art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>114</span><span style='color:black'>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}